ElementDescription: Have you ever been bullied at school or on school property?
Notes: 0 = No; 1 = Yes

ElementDescription: On an average school day, how many hours do you spend in front of a TV, computer, smartphone, or other electronic device watching shows or videos, playing games, accessing the internet, or using social media (also called ''screen time'')? Do not count time spent doing schoolwork.
Notes: 0 = Less than 1 hour; 1 = 1 to 2 hours; 2 = 2 to 3 hours; 3 = 3 to 4 hours; 4 = 4 to 5 hours; 5 = 5 or more hours

ElementDescription: How many times in a normal week do you play or exercise hard enough to make you sweat and breathe heavily?
Notes: 0 = Never; 1 = 1-2 times; 2 = 3-5 times; 3 = 6-7 times; 4 = 8 or more times

ElementDescription: During the past month, how often was your mental health not good (including stress, anxiety, and/or depression)?
Notes: 0 = Never; 1 = Rarely; 2 = Sometimes; 3 = Most of the time; 4 = Always

ElementDescription: Have you ever purposely hurt yourself without wanting to die?
Notes: 0=No; 1=Yes; -99=Decline to answer

ElementDescription: During the past 12 months, did you ever seriously consider attempting suicide?
Notes: 0=No; 1=Yes; -99=Decline to answer

ElementDescription: During the past 12 months, did you make a plan about how you would attempt suicide?
Notes: 0=No; 1=Yes; -99=Decline to answer

ElementDescription: During the past 12 months, how many times did you actually attempt suicide?
Notes: Number of attempts

ElementDescription: If you attempted suicide during the past 12 months, did any attempt result in an injury, poisoning, or overdose that had to be treated by a doctor or nurse?
Notes: 0=No; 1=Yes; -99=Decline to answer

ElementDescription: During the last 12 months, how many times did you do something to purposely hurt yourself without wanting to die, such as cutting or burning yourself on purpose?
Notes: Number of times
